						               													<description>Mensch &amp;#195;&amp;#164;rgere Dich nicht: ...noch mehr &amp;#195;&amp;#164;rgern &amp;#226;&amp;#128;&amp;#147; Kartenerweiterung Blau is an expansion deck of 55 cards that can be used in conjunction with Mensch &amp;#195;&amp;#164;rgere Dich nicht or any Pachisi clone. With these cards even more trouble is guaranteed for the players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After a player rolls the die and moves their pawn, they can draw a card and on a future turn, instead of rolling, they can choose to play a card from their hand. Cards allow, for instance, moving a pawn twelve spaces, passing everyone on the board, swapping two pawns, or taking other actions sure to frustrate their opponents. Of course they'll turn around and do the same to them. All's fair!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Kartenerweiterung Blau deck can be combined with the Kartenerweiterung Rot deck for more variety and fun.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
